snippet.title: Amber Heard Attacks LAPD For Releasing Footage Of Her In Court
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Supposedly Attacked The LAPD In Court After Footage Of Her Harassing Johnny Depp Was Released!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

Amber Heard subpoenas LAPD over 2016 domestic disturbance incident involving ex-husband Johnny Depp. That's quite a news! There has been some time since we heard something about Amber and Johnny Depp. It seems that after Johnny's victory, Amber hid and a mouse ate her tongue because until now she has been very quiet about it. However, we want to believe that after not having much evidence to help her win the case against her ex-husband, her legal team is plotting something to put Amber back in the lead in this case. What is happening? Now, what happened to Amber and her legal team?

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
